{"word":"H4843 - מָרַר - mârar - maw-rar' - Bitter","slug":"H4843","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָרַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mârar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-rar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bitter"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E8;&#x05E8; - ma&#x0302;rar</b> - <i>maw-rar'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>trickle</i> (see <a href=\"#/H4752\">H4752</a>); but used only as a denominative from <a href=\"#/H4751\">H4751</a>; to <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>bitter</i> (literally or figuratively): - (be, be in, deal, have, make) bitter (-ly, -ness), be moved with choler, (be, have sorely, it) grieved (-eth), provoke, vex."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4470\">H4470</a>, <a href=\"#/H4472\">H4472</a>, <a href=\"#/H4751\">H4751</a>, <a href=\"#/H4753\">H4753</a>, <a href=\"#/H4755\">H4755</a>, <a href=\"#/H4785\">H4785</a>, <a href=\"#/H4786\">H4786</a>, <a href=\"#/H4787\">H4787</a>, <a href=\"#/H4814\">H4814</a>, <a href=\"#/H4815\">H4815</a>, <a href=\"#/H4844\">H4844</a>, <a href=\"#/H4845\">H4845</a>, <a href=\"#/H4846\">H4846</a>, <a href=\"#/H4847\">H4847</a>, <a href=\"#/H4848\">H4848</a>, <a href=\"#/H8563\">H8563</a>"}]}